scene.message:
Yukino: There!{nl}
Just as you wished, we came!!{nl}
Michiko Matsudaira!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hand over the "chain key"{nl}
binding Toro and Kuroori!{nl}
By force, if it comes to it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Well, I meant to do it by{nl}
force from the start - your{nl}
sort won't hand it over{waitkey}quietly, will you?{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: What?! You?{nl}
You came here this quickly?{waitkey}{clearbox}Th-{wait_fr:30}the "Mirror Shard"?{nl}
Don't tell me you didn't{nl}
go get it? Oh!{wait_fr:30} Oh!? How!?{waitkey}{clearbox}At this rate!{wait_fr:30} At this rate!!{nl}
The "negative" power of human{nl}
emotion, source of my might!{waitkey}{clearbox}The power of "hatred" and{nl}
"anger" is - lacking!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Far too lacking!!{waitkey}{clearbox}No{wait_fr:30}, worse than that......{nl}
What is this? This unpleasant{nl}
feeling flooding into me?{waitkey}{clearbox}Wh-{wait_fr:30}what?{wait_fr:30} "Gratitude"?{nl}
"Friendship"?{nl}
Don't tell me they hold such{nl}
feelings even under torture?{waitkey}{clearbox}I-impossible!? You knew how{nl}
this tower works?{nl}
You did??{waitkey}{clearbox}No, that can't be!{nl}
My plan was supposed{nl}
to be perfect!{waitkey}{clearbox}The feeling every human holds -{nl}
"so long as I'm fine, who{nl}
cares about others"...{waitkey}{clearbox}No!{wait_fr:30} It's not so lofty{nl}
a thing as a feeling!{waitkey}{clearbox}Instinct!{wait_fr:30} Yes, my plan used{nl}
you humans' very instinct!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Why?{wait_fr:30} Why?? How can you try{nl}
to save others with no{nl}
reward at all?{waitkey}{clearbox}Michiko can't understand it!{nl}
At this rate! Like this!!{nl}
My power's far too lacking{waitkey}What am I to do?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Well, the usual me{nl}
would leave such fellows be{nl}
and go fetch the "Mirror{waitkey}Shard."{waitkey}{clearbox}Hmph! I don't know what you{nl}
schemed with your meager wits,{nl}
but you made one mistake.{waitkey}{clearbox}You truly angered me,{nl}
Kei Nanjo.{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't tell me you thought{nl}
you'd get away free after{nl}
such a fool of me?{waitkey}{clearbox}The sin of calling the great{nl}
Kei Nanjo a lapdog!{waitkey}{clearbox}You'll pay for it with your{nl}
death! Prepare yourself!!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Abandon my friends and{nl}
it'd stain my brilliant{nl}
record!!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's guys like you I just{nl}
can't forgive!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hurting Toro and the{nl}
Demon Kid!{nl}
Calling everyone mutts!{nl}
And above all!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Calling the great me a pet!{nl}
I'll pay you back for that{nl}
in full!{waitkey}Prepare yourself!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Heh-heh! Besides,{nl}
we don't need all 12{nl}
"Mirror Shards" - about{waitkey}8 is totally fine!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ayase doesn't care what{nl}
happens to Toro and Kuroori,{nl}
buuut{waitkey}{clearbox}an unpleasant woman like you{nl}
acting all high and mighty{waitkey}{clearbox}is, like, totally MMC,{nl}
y'know?{nl}
Get it?{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Kiiiii!{nl}
Shut up! Shut up!!{waitkey}Be quiet!! Hush!!{waitkey}{clearbox}So what are you saying?{nl}
That I am inferior to those{nl}
two ugly creatures??{waitkey}{clearbox}Beautiful me?? How can it be??{nl}
Ohh!! Oooh!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yes, the splendid plan I laid{nl}
was too highbrow for mutts{nl}
like you to grasp!{waitkey}{clearbox}Oooh! Ohh!! I should have{nl}
slaughtered you all the moment{nl}
you entered this tower!{waitkey}Ooooh!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: "Ow, ow," how noisy.{nl}
Hmph! You're no fur seal...{waitkey}{clearbox}But Ayase is right. Letting{nl}
a shard or two slip here{waitkey}won't shake our victory!{waitkey}{clearbox}A fiend like you we cannot{nl}
forgive, no matter what!{nl}
First, we'll defeat you!{waitkey}No mercy!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Michiko...{nl}
you're a poor loser.{waitkey}{clearbox}The more you wail, the more{nl}
your ugliness stands out...{waitkey}{clearbox}You should look at your own{nl}
face in a mirror right now.{waitkey}{clearbox}Heehee... it's hardly fit{nl}
to show to others.{waitkey}{clearbox}Indeed, as Ayase says, losing{nl}
a shard or two from this tower{waitkey}won't trouble us one bit.{waitkey}{clearbox}Let's end this idle chatter.{nl}
And the reason we came{waitkey}straight here...{waitkey}{clearbox}no matter how long we explain,{nl}
you'll never understand it.{waitkey}Now! Prepare yourself!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Kiii!{nl}
I will never, ever accept it!{waitkey}{clearbox}The "kindness" of the human{nl}
heart! "Friendship"!{nl}
"Trust"!{waitkey}{clearbox}Such things!{wait_fr:30} Such things!!{nl}
I'll prove they absolutely{nl}
do not exist in this world!{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll prove it with{nl}
your defeat!!{waitkey}{clearbox}"Lord Nemesis"...{nl}
be the armor that guards me!{nl}
"Lord Nemesis"...{waitkey}be the sword to destroy them!{waitkey}{clearbox}Come!{wait_fr:30} "Nemesis"!!{nl}
To my side!{nl}
"Nemesis power{wait_fr:30} build{waitkey}uuup!"{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: So you mean to summon{nl}
a Persona, do you?{nl}
Everyone! Here we go!{waitkey}Payback for Toro and Kuroori!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: So this looks like{nl}
Michiko's room.{waitkey}{clearbox}What awful taste, though.{nl}
What are these faces lined{waitkey}up on the wall??{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Ohohohoho!{nl}
Those faces are the remains{nl}
of humans who wouldn't{waitkey}obey me...{waitkey}{clearbox}And they're your future{nl}
selves, as well.{waitkey}{clearbox}Heehee... to gain five new{nl}
faces - what a wonderful{nl}
day today is!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho! How about it?{nl}
My collection?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is it to your liking?{waitkey}{clearbox}You filthy little thieves who{nl}
abandoned suffering friends,{nl}
driven by greed?{waitkey}{clearbox}It seems you did accept my{nl}
gift, the "Mirror Shard,"{nl}
after all.{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho! To fall so easily{nl}
into the trap I set!{waitkey}{clearbox}Lured by the bait of a single{nl}
"Mirror Shard,"{waitkey}{clearbox}you threw away with your own{nl}
hands your chance{nl}
to defeat me!{nl}
Ohohohoho!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What did you say?{nl}
We fell into a trap?{waitkey}{clearbox}What do you mean?{nl}
You! What did you do?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Fugah?{nl}
The great me, in a trap??{nl}
What's that mean?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, you! Explain yourself!!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ngh! What's this!{nl}
This hag! Just because Ayase{nl}
and friends took the shard,{waitkey}{clearbox}you're cornered and bluffing,{nl}
aren't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}You liar!! Just be quiet and{nl}
get beaten by Ayase and{nl}
friends!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Ohohohoho!{nl}
This "Tower of Nemesis"{waitkey}{clearbox}grows by absorbing humans'{nl}
"negative" emotions - "anger,"{nl}
"hatred," "despair"{waitkey}{clearbox}- as its energy. A "living{nl}
tower," you might say.{waitkey}{clearbox}And by taking the energy the{nl}
tower draws up into my own{nl}
body,{waitkey}{clearbox}I grow boundlessly stronger.{nl}
That was the mechanism.{nl}
Do you understand?{waitkey}{clearbox}Hehehe... the "sorrow" and{nl}
"anger" born from the pain{nl}
of those two ugly men,{waitkey}{clearbox}the "hatred" and "despair"{nl}
born of being abandoned by{nl}
the friends they trusted...{waitkey}{clearbox}Fwahahaha! All of it gave my{nl}
body such wonderful power!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohoho! If you'd resent{nl}
anyone, resent your own{nl}
lowly natures, you masses!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Quite the power!{nl}
And she's merely standing{nl}
there!{waitkey}{clearbox}This murderous surge of "qi"{nl}
bearing down on us!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Did Yokouchi and Kuroori's{nl}
"anger" and "hatred" truly{nl}
power her up...{waitkey}{clearbox}A blunder! To hand her power{nl}
right before our eyes...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What?!{nl}
This vicious wave?{waitkey}{clearbox}And Michiko's just{nl}
standing there...!{waitkey}{clearbox}The "anger" and "hatred" of{nl}
the two who were tortured{waitkey}{clearbox}have made Michiko's Power{nl}
so Big it's unmanageable...{waitkey}We were completely outwitted!{waitkey}{ret}

Michiko: Now, the five faces{nl}
of impudent little puppies{nl}
who defied "the Snow Queen"{waitkey}{clearbox}and made a fool of me...{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll add them to the faces{nl}
of the humans who once{nl}
betrayed me!{waitkey}{clearbox}Your "anger"!{wait_fr:30} Your "regret"!{nl}
Your "despair"!{wait_fr:30} Your "hatred"!{nl}
More!{wait_fr:30} More!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Bare your "negative" emotions,{nl}
your human instinct, and{nl}
come at me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Even that is, to me, an{nl}
irresistible feast!{waitkey}{clearbox}Khehehe! Hahahahaha!{nl}
Fwahahaha!{waitkey}{clearbox}"Lord Nemesis"...{nl}
be the armor that guards me!{nl}
"Lord Nemesis"...{waitkey}be the sword to destroy them!{waitkey}{clearbox}Come!{wait_fr:30} "Nemesis"!!{nl}
To my side!{nl}
"Nemesis power{wait_fr:30} build{waitkey}uuup!"{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Tch!{wait_fr:30} A Persona?{nl}
Everyone! No use grumbling{nl}
about what's done now!{waitkey}{clearbox}For now, let's deal with{nl}
this thing before us!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: So this looks like{nl}
Michiko's room.{waitkey}{clearbox}What awful taste, though.{nl}
What are these faces lined{waitkey}up on the wall??{waitkey}{ret}

