selves, as well.{waitkey}{clearbox}Heehee... to gain five new{nl}
faces - what a wonderful{nl}
day today is!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho! How about it?{nl}
My collection?{waitkey}{clearbox}Is it to your liking?{waitkey}{clearbox}Still, what a leisurely{nl}
arrival you've made!{waitkey}{clearbox}I grew quite tired of waiting!{waitkey}{clearbox}Ohohohoho! To fall so easily{nl}
into the trap I set!{waitkey}{clearbox}Lifting the tower's time{nl}
limit was the right call!{waitkey}{clearbox}Your chance to defeat me...{waitkey}{clearbox}you threw it away with your{nl}
own hands! Michiko can't{nl}
stop laughing! Ohohohoho!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What did you say?{nl}
We fell into a trap?{waitkey}{clearbox}What do you mean?{nl}
You! What did you do?!{waitkey}{ret}

