of those two ugly men,{waitkey}{clearbox}the "doubt" and "despair"{nl}
born of the uneasy thought{nl}
that trusted friends wouldn't come...{waitkey}{clearbox}Fwahahaha! All of it gave my{nl}
body such wonderful power!{waitkey}{clearbox}And plenty of it! All thanks{nl}
to you taking your time{nl}
getting here. My gratitude!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Quite the power!{nl}
